### VisionPulse API tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### All assets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/assets

### All events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events

### Quotes - all default MVP assets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/market/quotes?symbols=GOLD,SILVER,BTC,ETH,OIL,SPY,QQQ,NVDA

### Gold spot - should use Alpha Vantage GOLD_SILVER_SPOT, not GLD/ETF
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/market/quote/GOLD

### Silver spot - should use Alpha Vantage GOLD_SILVER_SPOT, not SLV/ETF
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/market/quote/SILVER

### Force Alpha route for metals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/market/quote/GOLD?provider=alpha

### Generate prediction
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/predictions/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt_cpi_us_001",
  "assetSymbol": "GOLD"
}
